      <title>随着投资者重新评估美国库存数据，油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-advance-investors-reassess-us-inventories-data-2024-03-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者重新评估最新的美国原油和汽油库存数据并重返购买模式，全球油价周四小幅上涨，从连续两个交易日的下跌中恢复过来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-advance-investors-reassess-us-inventories-data-2024-03-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 00:49:33 GMT</pubDate>
